## User Stories

- **As a user**, I want to enter a keyword so I can search for GIFs that match my mood.
- **As a user**, I want to see search results displayed in a clean, responsive grid so I can easily browse.
- **As a user**, I want feedback if no GIFs are found so I know something went wrong.
- **As a user**, I want the site to work well on both desktop and mobile devices.

